{
  "texts": [
    "It was shown that although the model was generally accurate, it produced harmful diets.",
    "These studies highlight the need for further investigation into LLM responses within the context of food and nutrition.",
    "Our results confirmed previous findings about the overall accuracy of ChatGPT and the instances of inaccurate responses.",
    "However, unlike the existing work, our study is not merely restricted to ChatGPT or the ZS prompting technique.",
    "We also focused on examining errors across various subcategories and mitigate them by employing prompting techniques (reasoning and ensemble) and external knowledge retrieval."
  ]
}